(262, 12, '_section_one_main_title', 'field_5c4f52a8b2a4c'),
(263, 12, 'section_one_paragraph', 'Generations ago, we planted ourselves here: farmers and manufacturers, life science experts and dreamers. The Indiana Uplands endures as a land of opportunity, from early color televisions to leading-edge advances in pharmaceuticals. Encounter our history at NSWC Crane, the world\'s third-largest naval installation, or at Cook Medical, the largest privately held medical device manufacturer in the country. See our progress through enterprising companies like Jasper Engines, Kimball, AECOM, Baxter, and General Dynamics. Determination rooted this land, and innovation makes it thrive.'),
