(360, 12, '_section_three_main_title', 'field_5c4f5f934033f'),
(361, 12, 'section_three_paragraph', 'At the heart of dozens of competitive industries, Uplands companies are showing the world what they\'re worth. Global, multinational corporations from GM and Catalent to Boston Scientific and SAIC. New technologies and industries grow and settle here every year, laying the groundwork for generations of future success while bolstering current business, competition, and family life. For new businesses and legacy companies, entrepreneurial endeavors and worldwide corporations, one thing is certain: In the Indiana Uplands, we are on the way UP.'),
