(369, 95, 'main_banner_text', 'In a region replete with talent and resources, Uplanders—from students to visionaries, artisans to entrepreneurs—are competitive and thriving here and worldwide. Uplands families, a dedicated workforce, and a tide of trailblazers call our 11 counties home: Home of industry and determination, innovation and creativity, good friends and reliable neighbors. Our home is Uplands Made.'),
