(1190, 30, '_main_banner_title', 'field_5c52167cce579'),
(1191, 30, 'main_banner_text', 'When the Uplander community bands together, we accomplish amazing things. Vineyards, state parks, and caves; family-friendly campgrounds and weekend lake getaways; exciting city attractions and world-class views—all paired with industries varying from defense and auto manufacturing to life sciences and limestone. We’re global competitors and home-grown neighbors. What’s UP in the Uplands? Just about everything you can imagine.'),
