(1361, 24, 'section_three_a_paragraph', 'Venture along I-69, the Midwestern highway that will eventually stretch from Canada to Mexico—with the Uplands neatly situated in the center. This breathtaking drive through rolling hills, robust farmland, and thriving cities will connect eight states to the heart of the Uplands.'),
