(2837, 493, '_section_two_title_a', 'field_5c5330f8a6405'),
(2838, 493, 'section_two_text_a', 'Groundbreaking research centers. Future-forward industry. Cohorts of creative entrepreneurs. In the Uplands, visionary leaders develop new businesses and test advanced technologies, forming a foundation for the opportunities of tomorrow. Automative advances, life-saving devices, defense technologies: we\'re equipped for any turn the market takes.'),
