(4072, 550, 'main_banner_text', 'Along the highways and byways of Indiana Uplands, dreams come alive. Across the 203,000 pristine acres of trails and campsites that form Hoosier National Forest; along the Lawrence Barn Quilt Trail and the stretches of shore of Lake Monroe; while sampling decades-aged Uplands wine, you’ll discover just what makes this land remarkable. From weekend to wonder, this is Uplands Made.'),
