(4856, 634, 'main_banner_image', '633'),
(4857, 634, '_main_banner_image', 'field_5c4f732171957'),
(4858, 634, 'main_banner_title', 'Living in the Uplands'),
(4859, 634, '_main_banner_title', 'field_5c4f732171995'),
(4860, 634, 'main_banner_text', 'When you encounter the Uplands’ combination of urban amenities with strong community ties, you’ll understand why so many people who come here want to stay. From fundraisers to foundations, educational opportunities to workforce growth initiatives, our neighbors, towns, and businesses are dedicated to ensuring you flourish.'),
(4861, 634, '_main_banner_text', 'field_5c4f7321719d2'),
(4862, 634, 'section_one_main_title', 'Happening at Home'),
(4863, 634, '_section_one_main_title', 'field_5c4f735c38b08'),
(4864, 634, 'section_one_paragraph', 'What\'s up in the Uplands? Local art galleries, farmers\' markets, historic theaters, artisan fairs, and sporting events for the whole family. Our neighbors cultivate strength and support for all. Come experience the Hoosier hospitality for which we\'re famous; we\'ll help you feel at home.'),
(4865, 634, '_section_one_paragraph', 'field_5c4f735c38b46'),
(4866, 634, 'section_one_image', '523'),
(4867, 634, '_section_one_image', 'field_5c4f735c38b83'),
(4868, 634, 'section_two_main_title', 'Education to Excellence'),
(4869, 634, '_section_two_main_title', 'field_5c4f73780a077'),
(4870, 634, 'section_two_paragraph', 'In the heart of the Uplands, education thrives. From our network of highly rated elementary and secondary schools to campuses of Indiana University, Ivy Tech, and Vincennes University Jasper Campus, students age 6 to 60 pursue their dreams every year. With ready school initiatives, STEM leadership training, and graduation and career coaching, every future you can imagine is starting right here.'),
(4871, 634, '_section_two_paragraph', 'field_5c4f73780a0b4'),
(4872, 634, 'section_two_featured_image', '525'),
(4873, 634, '_section_two_featured_image', 'field_5c4f73780a0f0'),
(4874, 635, 'main_banner_image', '602'),
(4875, 635, '_main_banner_image', 'field_5c520997bddd8'),
(4876, 635, 'main_banner_title', 'Weekend to Wonder'),
(4877, 635, '_main_banner_title', 'field_5c520997bddf0'),
(4878, 635, 'main_banner_text', 'Along the highways and byways of Indiana Uplands, dreams come alive. Across the 203,000 pristine acres of trails and campsites that form Hoosier National Forest; along the Lawrence Barn Quilt Trail and the stretches of shore of Lake Monroe; while sampling decades-aged Uplands wine, you’ll discover just what makes this land remarkable. From weekend to wonder, this is Uplands Made.'),
(4879, 635, '_main_banner_text', 'field_5c520997bde01'),
(4880, 635, 'section_one_title', 'Campgrounds and Courtyards'),
(4881, 635, '_section_one_title', 'field_5c520a4928f09'),
(4882, 635, 'section_one_paragraph', 'Luxurious West Baden Springs Resort. Bed and breakfast in small-town Nashville.  At every pace, for every family, in every community, you’ll encounter the home-grown hospitality that makes Uplanders proud.'),
(4883, 635, '_section_one_paragraph', 'field_5c520a8928f0b'),
(4884, 635, 'section_one_list', 'Enchanted Lake Lodge\r\nCanyon Inn\r\nBlueberry Hill Estate\r\nWinfield West B&amp;B\r\nFrench Lick Resort\r\nand more...!'),
(4885, 635, '_section_one_list', 'field_5c520a9828f0c'),
(4886, 635, 'section_two_title', 'Budget to Boutique'),
(4887, 635, '_section_two_title', 'field_5c520b712c85d'),
(4888, 635, 'section_two_paragraph', 'With the diversity of craft in the Uplands, take advantage of artisan candy and handcrafted Amish goods, farmers’ market finds and busy urban shopping centers, rustic antiques and locally sourced materials—all cornerstones of a broad and beautiful marketplace that says: I’m Uplands Made.'),
(4889, 635, '_section_two_paragraph', 'field_5c520b712c879'),
(4890, 635, 'section_two_list', 'Brown County Antique Mall\r\nCrane’s Leather and Shoe Shop\r\nNate’s Candy Jar\r\nNine Dragon Pottery &amp; Bonsai\r\nBlue Boy Chocolates\r\nFallen Leaf Books\r\nFox Hollow Gallery\r\nAnd MORE...!'),
