(4901, 635, '_section_four_title', 'field_5c520c9cc4cfc'),
(4902, 635, 'section_four_paragraph', 'Mountain explorers, cyclists, leaf peepers, music lovers, bird watchers, kayakers, hunters, listeners, swimmers, dip-your-toe-in-the-lake-ers—across the Uplands, your leisure is our pleasure. Whether it’s a visit to Salem Speedway, a weekend at Hoosier State Forest, a day exploring caves, or a raucous evening among basketball fans, your opportunities are as open as our rolling hills. Wander to wilderness: This is Uplands Made. '),
